OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779700299
OL,3,CHouseholds urged to boil water before
OL,4,Cdrinking for third day
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water continues to
OL,7,Furge people living across much of the
OL,8,FRhondda to boil their tap water before
OL,9,Fusing it to drink or cook for the
OL,10,Fthird day in a row.
OL,12,FIt follows an issue at its Maerdy
OL,13,FWater Treatment Works, which the
OL,14,Fcompany says has now been resolved,
OL,15,Fbut the notice remains in place until
OL,16,FWelsh Water are "satisfied that the
OL,17,Fwater quality downstream is safe."
OL,19,FThe boil water notice covers a large
OL,20,Farea of the Rhondda and wider Rhondda
OL,21,FCynon Taf area.
