OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779700299
OL,3,CHouseholds urged to boil water before
OL,4,Cdrinking for third day
OL,6,FIt comes as Wales has seen high
OL,7,Ftemperatures over the Bank Holiday
OL,8,Fweekend.
OL,10,FThree bottled water stations have been
OL,11,Fset up in the area, which will be open
OL,12,Fovernight. They are based in:
OL,14,FWelsh Water says it is consulting with
OL,15,FRhondda Cynon Taf council to decide if
OL,16,Ffurther stations will be needed. It
OL,17,Falso says it's delivering bottled
OL,18,Fwater to its most vulnerable customers
OL,19,Fand care homes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
