OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779700299
OL,3,CHouseholds urged to boil water before
OL,4,Cdrinking for third day
OL,6,FWelsh Water said customers who are
OL,7,Fimpacted are being sent a text. You
OL,8,Fcan check if your area is affected
OL,9,Fusing the postcode checker here.
OL,11,FSteve Wilson, Chief Operations Officer
OL,12,Ffor Welsh Water, told ITV Wales that
OL,13,Fpublic health and safety remains the
OL,14,Fcompany's "absolute priority."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
