FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779700299
OL,3,CHouseholds urged to boil water before
OL,4,Cdrinking for third day
OL,6,FHe told ITV Wales, "We haven't got a
OL,7,Ftimeline currently, as we're
OL,8,Fcontinuing to take samples from the
OL,9,Fnetwork and monitor the water quality.
OL,10,FIt is a very long network... and it's
OL,11,Fimportant to us to make sure that we
OL,12,Fcan test the quality in the network
OL,13,Fand we're assured that it is safe
OL,14,Fbefore we're able to lift this notice.
OL,16,F"Some of these tests take quite a lot
OL,17,Fof hours as well to be analysed in the
OL,18,Flab, and that's what's taking the
OL,19,Ftime. I thank customers for bearing
OL,20,Fwith us at this time. We are trying to
OL,21,Fget this resolved as quick as we can."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
