PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779700299
OL,3,CHouseholds urged to boil water before
OL,4,Cdrinking for third day
OL,6,FIn a statement on Sunday afternoon,
OL,7,FWelsh Water said: "Following
OL,8,Finvestigation by our operational
OL,9,Fteams, the issue affecting the
OL,10,Fchemical dosing process at the Maerdy
OL,11,Ftreatment works has now been fixed and
OL,12,Fwater from the site is re-entering the
OL,13,Fnetwork.
OL,15,F"This is an important step forward in
OL,16,Fresolving the incident safely.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
