FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1779700299
OL,3,CHouseholds urged to boil water before
OL,4,Cdrinking for third day
OL,6,F"As a precaution, the boil water
OL,7,Fnotice remains in place and we ask
OL,8,Fthat you continue to follow guidance
OL,9,Fand boil tap water before drinking,
OL,10,Fbrushing teeth, preparing food or
OL,11,Fmaking ice until further notice."
